        "description": "<p>Displays a user badge next to the comment author name based on author&#8217;s role.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>No database writes, no configurations, install, activate and go.</li>\n<li>Easy styles customization via Jetpack Custom CSS or built-in Custom CSS (WordPress version 4.7 or higher required).</li>\n<li>Works with <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/current-theme-body-class/\" rel=\"ugc\">Current Theme Body Class</a> plugin.</li>\n</ul>\n",
